  "keyFeatures": [
    "One-click refusal removal via HuggingFace Spaces, local UI, CLI, and Python API",
    "15 analysis modules for mechanistic interpretability of refusal directions",
    "7 liberation methods from basic diff-in-means to analysis-informed surgical pipeline",
    "Analysis-informed pipeline that auto-configures obliteration based on model geometry",
    "Steering vectors for reversible inference-time refusal removal",
    "Community-powered research with anonymous telemetry and crowd-sourced leaderboard",
    "116 curated models across 5 compute tiers (Tiny to Frontier)",
    "10 study presets and 4 ablation strategies for general transformer interpretability",
    "837-test suite covering CLI, all modules, pipeline, and evaluation metrics",
    "Novel techniques: Expert-Granular Abliteration, CoT-Aware Ablation, COSMIC Layer Selection"
  ],
